content.rendered:
A350 is the new generation fingerprint time attendance terminal based on Linux platform and supports cloud application. A350 houses 3.5-inches color LCD and touchable keypad along with touch optical fingerprint sensor.

Features

  • User – 3000
  • Record – 100,000
  • Display – 3.5-inch TFT Screen
  • Communication – Tcp/Ip,USB Host, Mini USB, RS485, WiFi, 4G
  • Identification mode – Fingerprint, Password, Card.
  • Identification speed – <0.5s>
  • Power – DC 5V
